he subsequently held global product line business development roles out of houston texas and headed schlumberger businesses in egypt east africa and east mediterranean more recently mr chariag occupied the position of marketing vice president for europe africa and the cis before being appointed president of well services in his last role with schlumberger he was in charge of hse security global regulatory compliance risk management and global citizenship mr chariag holds a bachelor of science degree in petroleum engineering from the university of texas baker hughes provides reservoir consulting drilling formation evaluation completion and production products and services to the worldwide oil and gas industry contact gary r flaharty 3 3939 h gene shiels 3 39 source baker hughes incorporated  3 contact gary r flaharty 33939 or h gene shiels 339 both of baker hughes incorporated web site httpwwwbakerhughescom  bhi co baker hughes incorporated st texas in oil gas uti su pr  da56  566 3 3 edt httpwwwprnewswirecom related informationadditional resourceswe look forward to helping you and will contact you as soon as possibleplease note this form is for processing product or service requests from customers for all careers or employment inquiries please contact the talent acquisition teamclose select a region africa asia pacific canada europe gulf of mexico latin america middle east russia caspian us land select a product line reservoir services drilling evaluation completions well interventions production pressure pumping process and pipeline services downstream chemicals specialty chemicals customer training other please specify in message first name last name email addressi would like someone to call me backphone number company message emailcancel belgacem chariag  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in belgacem chariag president global operations at baker hughes incorporated view full profile are you belgacem ch